{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "第三回\"死亡之前\"讲述决战前夜荒漠中的三方势力交锋。轩辕开山在荒漠中准备夜战，被田灵子主动搭讪。田灵子身材娇小却妩媚成熟，有过六任老公皆死，帐篷中养着四个习武当剑阵的男孩。两人互相试探，轩辕开山被田灵子的魅力吸引却被其武力震慑。正在此时，牧羊儿现身——一个极高极瘦的侏儒，穿褐色连帽长袍，湛蓝眼睛，声音沙哑甜蜜而诡秘恐怖。四个男孩拔剑进攻却被牧羊儿瞬间击杀，无人看见其出手。牧羊儿以绝对武力威慑轩辕和田灵子，三人达成临时同盟，准备联手对付今夜子时的对手。章末提及丁丁正准备穿越荒漠进入死亡，为下一章的决战埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "小鬼，你是干什么的？到这里来干什么？你不怕野狼把你吃了？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "小鬼？你说我是小鬼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "轩辕开山，你今年才三十三岁，就敢说我是小鬼？你知不知道在我六个老公里，年纪最小的一个都比你大十岁。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "我知道你是谁了，你一定就是那个要命的田灵子。幸好我也知道你只会要你老公的命，否则我早就已经像一只中了箭的兔子一样逃走。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "现在我才明白你那些老公怎么死的了，如果我是你老公，我也一样会死在你手里。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "可是我却看不透你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "我已经注意你四五天了，从你第一天来的时候，我就已经开始注意你了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "这四五天来我发现你把那附近每一个可作战的地方都观察的非常仔细，甚至连那里土质的柔软或坚硬都了解得非常透彻，甚至连那地区风向的变化也摸透了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "我本来一直以为你是一个粗枝大叶的人，想不到你居然这么细心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "粗枝大叶的男人也一样想活下去，不想死的人在这种生死决战之前怎么能不细心？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "能够让女人青春永驻的方法有很多种，我发现其中最有效的一种就是年轻漂亮的小男孩。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "我看得出你这种方法不但有效，而且有趣。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "所以等你再老一点的时候，你也不妨找几个漂亮的小姑娘来试验试验。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "我不喜欢小姑娘，我只喜欢你这样的女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "我听说高大魁伟的男人，都喜欢欺负娇小的女人。我也听说过，被你欺负过的女孩子可真不少。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "你怕不怕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "怕什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "你怕不怕我强奸你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "我知道你不会做这种傻事的，你自己也应该知道，你根本没有把握能制得住我。何况这些小鬼也不是好惹的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "他们的年纪虽然不大，却都已经学会了两极四仪剑阵。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "你大概也听说过，我的第五任老公是武当派中极有名望的一位名宿高手。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "我服了你了，我真不敢动你。这也是你运气好，遇见的是我。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "如果你遇见的是那个牧羊儿，现在你已经被赤条条的绑在柱子上了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "你见过牧羊儿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "我没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "那末你怎么知道他会对我有兴趣？你怎么知道被赤条条绑在柱子上的人不是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "我曾经听一个很可靠的消息来源说，她是个比我更娇小的女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "你也应该知道娇小的女人，最喜欢欺负的也就是你这种魁伟高大的男人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "如果她真的来了，会用什么方法对付你？我简直连想都不敢想。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "小轩辕，你用不着害怕，小田田，你也用不着高兴。我要对付你们的法子，绝对是一样的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "男人和女人我全都喜欢，所以你们全都用不着担心。我对付男人和女人的法子都一定完全公平。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "不管怎么样，你既然已经来了，就应该先宽衣坐下，喝一杯酒。我们总是同一条线上的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "那么你就不应该请我宽衣了，我脱下衣服来，通常都会让人吓一跳的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "不管男人和女人都会吓一跳。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "我想我们不会。我相信轩辕大兄见到的女人已经够多了，我见过的女人也不会太少。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "好。那么我就恭敬不如从命了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "现在我已经宽衣了。我是不是已经可以坐下来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "请坐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "我是不是应该坐在主人旁边？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "小轩辕，你有没有什么意见？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "我没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "你是不是已经开始有点佩服我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "好像已经有一点。我只奇怪你手里的鞭子到哪里去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "对付这种小垃圾，我还要用鞭子？等到我要用鞭子的时候，要对付的至少也是你这种人。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "text": "你呢？你有什么意见？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_ling_zi",
      "speaker_name": "田灵子",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "我有什么意见？难道你以为我会喜欢一堆垃圾？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "这么样看起来，我们三个人的想法好像已经有点沟通了。我相信你们现在都已经完全明白，要对付今天晚上那个对手，我们自己的思想一定要完全一致。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "那个人绝不是个容易对付的人，可是你们如果能绝对接纳我的意见，我保证他绝不会活过今夜子时。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕开山",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "最重要的一点是，不管我要你们做什么，你们都不能反对。否则你们两位的咽喉很可能已经先被割断。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_kai_shan",
      "text": "在这个情况下，如果我还觉得有什么不满意，那我就简直是不知好歹的畜生了。现在距离子时还有一个多时辰，我们为什么不好好的轻松一下，等着那个人来送死？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
